data.description: Over half an acre in Fleming Island and no CDD fees! Well maintained all brick 5/4 home is great for a large family and within walking distance to Paterson Elementary. This home even has space for your RV or boat with the large driveway. Roof 2020, both HVACs 2019, Water Heater 2020, new quiet close garage door 2019.  No pets have lived here for those with allergies, just beautiful new floors in most of the downstairs. Corian counters with granite island in the kitchen. This home comes with a man cave, game room upstairs with full bath, fenced rear yard and also has ADA sized hallways and doorways if needed. The storage room upstairs could be a craft room. The alley behind is part of the property with a 15' wooded buffer behind.  Please add to your list as a must see.  Welcome Home!
